         <category>Getting Started with eMod</category>
         <ttm:title>Corporate Information Screen</ttm:title>
         <ttm:desc>Confirm your Corporate Information before proceeding. Your Corporate Information is pulled directly from the System for Award Management, (SAM). Therefore, if incorrect, Corporate Information must be corrected outside the eOffer/eMod system.
         </ttm:desc>
